   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>6 artabai of wheat as seed allowance, 78 artabai of wheat for the whole, 40 drachmai as the price for green fodder. For the 2nd year, 12 artabai of vegetable seed, clean, by the four-choinix measure of the granary of Likis in the village of Talei. And in the 3rd year, 48 silver drachmai and 12 artabai of vegetable seed. (The lessee) may sow the land with whatever crops he may choose.</ab>
